#. Tag: title
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripción"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning touch typing. It helps you learn to "
"type on a keyboard quickly and correctly. Every finger has it's place on the "
"keyboard with associated keys to press."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; es un programa para aprender mecanografía. Le ayudará a "
"aprender mecanografía en un teclado de forma rápida y correcta. Cada dedo "
"tiene su lugar en el teclado con teclas asociadas para pulsar."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; helps you learn to touch type by providing you with text to "
"train on, and adjusts to different levels depending on how good you are. It "
"can display which key to press next, and correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; le ayuda a aprender mecanografía proporcionándole un texto "
"para practicar, y a ajustar diferentes niveles dependiendo de lo bueno que "
"sea. Puede mostrar qué tecla pulsar a continuación y corregir el dedo a "
"utilizar."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "This application is part of the official &kde; education module."
msgstr "Esta aplicación es parte del módulo educativo oficial de &kde;."

